name: Kira 'Spine' Valerius
description: A heavily augmented corporate agent, Kira is encased in a sleek exoskeleton studded with razor-sharp metallic spines. Her movements are precise and deliberate, suggesting years of combat training.

flavor.rationale: Kira was assigned to protect the entrance of Zenith-9's highest security data center after a recent breach. She is under strict orders not to allow unauthorized access, and will use lethal force if necessary.
